## Core Workflow: Spec Before Code

```
EXPLORE → SPEC → IMPLEMENT → VERIFY → ARCHIVE
```

| Phase | Output file | Notes |
|-------|-------------|-------|
| Explore | `.dev/specs/[feature]-context.md` | Map of relevant code |
| Spec | `.dev/specs/[feature]-spec.md` | What to build and why |
| Implement | git commits | Follow spec, commit often |
| Verify | `.dev/handoffs/[feature]-review.md` | Claude preferred |
| Archive | `.dev/handoffs/current-state.md` | Update state |

